      "content": "it's not just a \"tough time\" though. it feels deeper than that. like the actual substance of who i am is gone. people always say \"it gets better\" or \"you'll find your spark again,\" but what if it doesn't? what if the tragedy is just that the story is finished and i'm just... dragging out the epilogue?",
