    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "maybe. but there's something so exhausting about just waiting for a shift that never comes. it feels like i'm just playing a role in a play that should have ended three acts ago. doesn't it ever feel like there's a certain dignity in just... accepting when a chapter is over, instead of forcing it to keep going?",
